\c 16
\p
\v 1 Zvino vakapinza areka yaMwari, ndokuiisa pakati petende Dhavhidhi raaiva aiwaridzira. Zvino vakapa zvipo zvinopiswa nezvipo zvekuyananisa pamberi paMwari.
\v 2 Dhavhidhi wakati aguma kupa zvipo zvinopiswa nezvipo zvekuyananisa, wakaropafadza vanhu muzita raJehovha.
\v 3 Ndokugovera umwe neumwe waIsraeri, kubva kumurume kusvika kumukadzi, kune umwe neumwe rofu rechingwa, nenhindi yenyama, nechingwa chezvibereko zvemuzambiringa zvakaomeswa.
\p
\v 4 Zvino wakagadza vashumiri veVaRevhi, pamberi peareka yaJehovha, nekurangarira nekuvonga nekukudza Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri:
\v 5 Asafi musoro\x + 6.39.\x*, uye wepiri kwaari Zekariya\x + 15.18.\x*, Jeiyeri, naShemiramoti, naJehiyeri, naMatitia, naEriabhu, naBhenaya, naObhedhi-Edhomu, naJeiyeri, vane mitengeranwa\x + 15.16.\x* uye nembira\x + 15.16.\x*; Asafi ndokuridza nemakandira\x + 15.16.\x*.
\v 6 Zvino Bhenaya naJahazieri vapristi \add vairidza\add* nehwamanda rinhi narinhi pamberi peareka yesungano yaMwari\x + 15.24.\x*.
\s Rwiyo rwaDhavhidhi
\p
\v 7 Nezuva iro ipapo Dhavhidhi wakapa kekutanga \add pisarema iri\add* kuvonga Jehovha\x + 2 Sam. 22.1. 23.1.\x* neruoko rwaAsafi nehama dzake\x + 6.39.\x*:
\p
\v 8 Vongai Jehovha\x + Map. 105.1-15.\x*; danai zita rake\x + Isa. 12.4.\x*; zivisai zviito zvake pakati pevanhu\x + Map. 145.11.\x*.
\v 9 Muimbirei, mumuimbire mapisarema; rondedzerai pamusoro pemabasa ake ese anoshamisa\x + Vato. 5.10.\x*.
\v 10 Zvirumbidzei muzita rake dzvene; ngaifare moyo yevanotsvaka Jehovha.
\v 11 Tsvakai Jehovha nesimba rake; tsvakai chiso chake rinhi narinhi\x + Map. 24.6. 27.8.\x*.
\v 12 Rangarirai zvishamiso zvake zvaakaita\x + Map. 77.11. 143.5.\x*, zviratidzo zvake, nemitongo yemuromo wake\x + Eki. 4.21. 7.3. 11.9,10. Map. 78.43.\x*;
\v 13 imwi mbeu yaIsraeri, muranda wake, imwi vana vaJakove vasanangurwa vake.
\p
\v 14 Ndiye Jehovha Mwari wedu; mitongo yake iri pasi pese\x + Isa. 26.9.\x*.
\v 15 Rangarirai sungano yake nekusingaperi, shoko raakaraira kumarudzi churu;
\v 16 yaakaita naAbhurahama\x + Gen.. 17.2. 22.16. 26.3. 28.13. 35.11. Ruk. 1.73. VaHeb. 6.17.\x*, nemhiko yake kuna Isaka\x + Gen.. 17.2. 22.16. 26.3. 28.13. 35.11. Ruk. 1.73. VaHeb. 6.17.\x*;
\v 17 uye wakazvisimbisira Jakove kuva mutemo, kuna Israeri kuva sungano yekusingaperi;
\v 18 achiti: Ndichapa kwauri nyika yeKenani, mujenya wenhaka yenyu\x + Gen.. 13.15. 15.18-21.\x*;
\v 19 pamaiva vashoma pauwandu, hongu muri vashoma\x + Det. 7.7. 26.5.\x*, uye muri vatorwa mairi\x + VaHeb. 11.9.\x*.
\v 20 Zvino vakafamba-famba kubva kurudzi kuenda kurudzi, uye kubva kuushe kuenda kune rumwe rudzi.
\v 21 Haana kutendera munhu kuvaitira zvakaipa\x + Gen.. 35.5.\x*; zvirokwazvo wakatsiura madzimambo nekuda kwavo\x + Gen.. 12.17. 20.3.\x*;
\v 22 \add achiti\add*: Musabata vazodzwa vangu, uye musatadzira vaporofita vangu\x + Gen.. 20.7.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Imbirai Jehovha, pasi pose; paridzirai ruponeso rwake zuva nezuva\x + Map. 96.1-13.\x*;
\v 24 rondedzerai kubwinya kwake pakati pevahedheni, mabasa ake anoshamisa pakati pemarudzi ose.
\v 25 Nokuti mukuru Jehovha, uye anofanira kurumbidzwa zvikuru\x + Map. 145.3. 2 Sam. 22.4.\x*; iye anotyisa kupfuura vamwari vese\x + Map. 95.3.\x*.
\v 26 Nokuti vamwari vese vemarudzi zvifananidzo\x + Rev. 19.4.\x*; asi Jehovha wakaita matenga\x + Map. 115.15. Isa. 42.5. 44.24. Jer. 10.11,12.\x*.
\v 27 Rukudzo nekubwinya zviri pamberi pake; simba nemufaro zviri panzvimbo yake\x + Ezi. 6.16. Neh. 8.10.\x*.
\v 28 Ipai Jehovha, imwi mhuri dzemarudzi, ipai Jehovha rukudzo nesimba\x + Map. 29.1.\x*.
\v 29 Ipai Jehovha rukudzo rwezita rake\x + Map. 29.2.\x*; uisai chipo, uyai pamberi pake; namatai kuna Jehovha pakunaka kweutsvene\x + 2 Makor. 20.21. Map. 29.2. Map. 110.3. Zvir. 14.28. Map. 96.9.\x*.
\v 30 Dedera pamberi pake, nyika yose; uye nyika yakasimbiswa, haingazungunuswi.
\p
\v 31 Matenga ngaafare, nenyika ngaipembere\x + Isa. 49.13.\x*; nepakati pendudzi ngavati: Jehovha anotonga\x + Map. 93.1. 97.1. 99.1. Isa. 52.7. Zvak. 11.15,17. 19.6.\x*.
\v 32 Gungwa ngaritinhire, nekuzara kwaro; sango ngarifare, nezvese zviri mariri\x + Map. 98.7.\x*.
\v 33 Ipapo miti yesango ichaimba nemufaro pamberi paJehovha; nokuti anouya kuzotonga nyika.
\p
\v 34 Vongai Jehovha; nokuti wakanaka; nokuti nyasha dzake dziri\add po\add* nekusingaperi\x + 16.41. Map. 106.1. 107.1. 118.1. 136.1.\x*.
\v 35 Zvino muti: Tiponesei, Mwari weruponeso rwedu, uye mutiunganidze, mutisunungure pamarudzi, kuti \add ti\add*vonge zita renyu dzvene, kuti \add ti\add*zvikudze nerumbidzo yenyu\x + Map. 106.47,48.\x*.
\p
\v 36 Ngaakudzwe Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri, kubva pakusingaperi kusvika pakusingaperi\x + Map. 41.13.\x*. Vanhu vese ndokuti: Ameni; ndokurumbidza Jehovha\x + Det. 27.15.\x*.
\s Tabhenekari inochengetwa paGibhiyoni
\p
\v 37 Zvino wakasiyapo pamberi peareka yesungano yaJehovha Asafi nehama dzake, kuti vashumire pamberi peareka rinhi narinhi\x + 16.4,5.\x* zvenyaya yezuva pazuva rayo\x + 2 Makor. 31.16.\x*.
\v 38 NaObhedhi-Edhomu pamwe nehama dzavo, makumi matanhatu nevasere; naObhedhi-Edhomu mwanakomana waJedhutuni, naHosa, vave vachengeti vemasuwo\x + 26.10.\x*;
\v 39 naZadhoki mupristi, nehama dzake vapristi\x + 15.11.\x*, pamberi petabhenakeri yaJehovha panzvimbo yakakwirira yaiva paGibhiyoni\x + 1 Madz. 3.4.\x*;
\v 40 kuti vape Jehovha zvipo zvinopiswa rinhi narinhi mangwanani nemadeko paaritari yezvipiriso zvinopiswa\x + Eki. 27.1.\x*, nepazvese zvakanyorwa mumurairo waJehovha waakaraira Israeri\x + Eki. 29.38,39,41. Num.. 28.3,4.\x*;
\v 41 uye pamwe navo Hemani\x + 6.33.\x* naJedhutuni\x + 16.38,42. 6.44. 25.1,3,6. 2 Makor. 29.14.\x* nevamwe vaiva vasarudzwa, vakarehwa nemazita kuvonga Jehovha\x + Num.. 1.17.\x*; nokuti nyasha dzake \add dziripo\add* nekusingaperi\x + 16.34. 2 Makor. 5.13. 7.3,6. 20.21. Ezi. 3.11. Jer. 33.11.\x*;
\v 42 uye pamwe navo Hemani\x + 6.33.\x* naJedhutuni\x + 38,42. 6.44. 25.1,3,6. 2 Makor. 29.14.\x* \add ne\add*hwamanda nemakandira\x + 2 Makor. 5.13.\x* zveavo vanozviridza, nemidziyo yekuimba zvaMwari\x + 2 Makor. 5.13.\x*; uye vanakomana vaJedhutuni vaiva pasuwo\x + 16.38.\x*.
\v 43 Vanhu vese ndokuenda umwe neumwe kumba kwake; Dhavhidhi ndokudzoka kuzoropafadza imba yake\x + 2 Sam. 6.19,20.\x*.